1
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:15,779
Here's a breaking news.

2
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:17,580
Ye Zhimei, the heiress of Chenghai Group,

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:18,719
and her newlywed husband

4
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:21,299
were caught in extreme sea conditions

5
00:00:21,299 --> 00:00:22,660
due to a sudden storm while diving yesterday.

6
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:24,619
They were rescued by some unidentified good Samaritans.

7
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,159
According to the hospital,

8
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:28,760
Miss Ye suffered a head injury in the accident,

9
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,740
which may cause temporary blindness.

10
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:32,139
Zhimei.

11
00:00:50,719 --> 00:00:51,399
Zhimei.

12
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:55,539
Zhimei.

13
00:00:58,359 --> 00:00:58,940
Zhi Mei.

14
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,440
Wu Xi.

15
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:03,920
Is that you?

16
00:01:33,059 --> 00:01:34,280
I'll be your eyes.

17
00:01:34,699 --> 00:01:35,259
This way.

18
00:01:35,459 --> 00:01:36,339
Honey.

19
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:39,559
What's the surprise you said?

20
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:44,860
I couldn't find

21
00:01:45,839 --> 00:01:46,959
the ring in the sea.

22
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:49,699
But this one

23
00:01:51,699 --> 00:01:52,959
is designed by me.

24
00:01:53,679 --> 00:01:54,940
It's warm like you,

25
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,339
just like I'm always by your side.

26
00:02:00,419 --> 00:02:01,500
Do you like it?

27
00:02:01,759 --> 00:02:02,619
You...

28
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,100
You actually had our ring redesigned.

29
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,259
I like it.

30
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,180
By the way,

31
00:02:26,239 --> 00:02:27,019
the police

32
00:02:27,019 --> 00:02:29,120
asked us to sign a new accident report,

33
00:02:31,819 --> 00:02:33,259
which needs our confirmation.

34
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:35,100
Do you want me to read it to you?

35
00:02:35,859 --> 00:02:36,919
No need, honey.

36
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,519
I trust you.

37
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:39,699
Okay.

38
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,539
Come on.

39
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:50,259
Where is it?

40
00:02:52,380 --> 00:02:53,060
Here.

41
00:02:59,739 --> 00:03:00,859
Sir, madam,

42
00:03:01,019 --> 00:03:01,919
the guests have arrived.

43
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,519
I'll go get ready.

44
00:03:05,799 --> 00:03:06,699
Hurry up.

45
00:03:06,699 --> 00:03:08,259
Don't keep the guests waiting.

46
00:03:09,699 --> 00:03:10,500
Okay.

47
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:49,079
I...

48
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,799
I can see.

49
00:03:54,799 --> 00:03:55,940
I can see.

50
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:58,979
Wu Xi, Wu Xi, Wu Xi.

51
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:05,180
Death certification.

52
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,919
Whose death?

53
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:24,939
No, no way.

54
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,760
My husband was just here.

55
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:27,960
Do you like it?

56
00:04:28,619 --> 00:04:30,059
Why did he want me to sign this?

57
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,919
Happy anniversary.

58
00:04:59,999 --> 00:05:00,799
Zhi Mei.

59
00:05:26,619 --> 00:05:27,640
Happy anniversary.

60
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:31,419
Happy anniversary.

61
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:44,119
He's not Wu Xi.

62
00:05:44,299 --> 00:05:46,700
Who is he?

63
00:05:59,379 --> 00:06:01,460
Mrs. Yu lost her ring. Search carefully.

64
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:02,280
Okay.

65
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:02,919
Okay.

66
00:06:05,919 --> 00:06:08,179
Qingmei, congratulations.

67
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:09,739
Wu Xi loves you so much.

68
00:06:14,439 --> 00:06:16,280
Zhi... Zhi Mei.

69
00:06:16,679 --> 00:06:17,840
Oh, my bad.

70
00:06:17,979 --> 00:06:19,479
I'm drunk.

71
00:06:20,039 --> 00:06:22,780
Qingmei? You got the name wrong.

72
00:06:23,179 --> 00:06:25,200
Who's this guy? So unprofessional.

73
00:06:25,999 --> 00:06:27,679
Zhi, you must be tired.

74
00:06:27,999 --> 00:06:28,999
I'll take you back to rest.

75
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:34,419
What's wrong?

76
00:06:34,539 --> 00:06:35,320
My ring.

77
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,739
Where is my ring?

78
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,439
Honey, help me find it.

79
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,600
There are so many people today.

80
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:41,919
What if I can't find it?

81
00:06:42,859 --> 00:06:44,220
Don't worry. I'll help you find it.

82
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,200
I'll take you back first.

83
00:06:45,939 --> 00:06:46,679
Chairman Wu, I'll find it.

84
00:06:46,679 --> 00:06:47,859
It's okay. You go ahead.

85
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,220
[He has my phone.]

86
00:06:53,619 --> 00:06:55,799
[He cut off my way to ask for help.]

87
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:57,999
[I can't trust anyone in the manor.]

88
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:00,160
[I must get out of here first.]

89
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,299
[Fire alarm!]

90
00:07:16,299 --> 00:07:17,479
[Put out the fire!]

91
00:07:19,059 --> 00:07:19,640
Zhi Mei.

92
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:42,020
Sir, there's no fire.

93
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,100
But the lady is missing.

94
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:47,260
Zhi Mei.

95
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,660
Where are you?

96
00:08:04,739 --> 00:08:05,439
Zhi Mei.

97
00:08:07,619 --> 00:08:08,239
Zhi Mei!

98
00:08:08,539 --> 00:08:10,939
Open the door, it's me, Zhi Mei!

99
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,600
Zhi Mei, be careful!

100
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:15,619
Zhi Mei!

101
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:23,900
Zhi Mei!

102
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:25,999
Zhi Mei!

103
00:08:29,979 --> 00:08:31,460
Zhi Mei, it's me, it's me!

104
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:32,039
Let go of me!

105
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:32,439
Zhi Mei!

106
00:08:32,439 --> 00:08:32,859
Who are you?

107
00:08:32,859 --> 00:08:34,100
It's me, it's me!

108
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:37,739
Honey, honey, is that you?

109
00:08:41,420 --> 00:08:43,100
Zhi Mei, shouldn't you be in the bedroom?

110
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,779
Why are you here?

111
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,359
Honey,

112
00:08:47,499 --> 00:08:49,399
I heard a loud noise

113
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,739
and I've been looking for you.

114
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:52,200
But I couldn't find you.

115
00:08:52,659 --> 00:08:53,960
I'm so scared.

116
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:55,019
It's okay,

117
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:56,499
it's okay.

118
00:08:59,259 --> 00:09:00,060
Fang Jie,

119
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:02,159
tomorrow, seal all the windows

120
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,659
in the house.

121
00:09:05,499 --> 00:09:06,460
Yes, sir.

122
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:27,960
Honey,

123
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,499
are you still there?

124
00:09:29,999 --> 00:09:30,800
I'm here.

125
00:09:47,359 --> 00:09:48,159
Honey,

126
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,960
you must be in a lot of pain today.

127
00:09:52,619 --> 00:09:53,759
It's all my fault.

128
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:56,159
It's okay.

129
00:09:58,899 --> 00:09:59,619
Remember,

130
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:02,820
no matter what happens in the future, don't run around.

131
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,200
Because wherever you go,

132
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,460
I will always find you.

133
00:10:10,460 --> 00:10:13,040
[This voice sounds just like Wu Xi's.]

134
00:10:13,739 --> 00:10:14,320
[Every intonation]

135
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,340
[is measured.]

136
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,300
[No wonder it could fool me.]

137
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:19,300
Alright, it's getting late.

138
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:20,340
Time to sleep.

139
00:10:26,659 --> 00:10:28,100
I'm not going anywhere tonight.

140
00:10:29,999 --> 00:10:31,100
I'll just stay here with you.

141
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,200
Come on.

142
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:43,879
We can't let this special day be ruined.

143
00:10:47,019 --> 00:10:51,560
Let's celebrate it all over again, shall we?

144
00:10:55,899 --> 00:10:56,499
Okay.
